			In the final stage of a long decline, Hindustan Motors announced in May that it would suspend production of the Ambassador, a car that was once synonymous with style and status.<a href="//india.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/06/27/an-icon-of-indian-roads-is-set-out-to-pasture/" class="more-link">Read&#160;more&#8230;</a></p>
		</div>
		</div><!-- end Recent Posts side tool -->
